## Suggested Improvements

### 1. 🔒 Security Headers
**Problem:** No HTTP security headers are set, leaving the app vulnerable to clickjacking, MIME sniffing, XSS, etc.

```js
const helmet = require('helmet');
app.use(helmet()); // Sets X-Content-Type-Options, X-Frame-Options, HSTS, CSP, etc.
```

