| Priority | Issue | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| 🔴 Critical | No auth on `/users` | Add authentication middleware |
| 🔴 Critical | Missing security headers | Add `helmet` |
| 🔴 Critical | No rate limiting | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| 🟠 High | No global error handler | Add `(err, req, res, next)` middleware |
| 🟠 High | No body size limits | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| 🟠 High | Hardcoded port | Use `process.env.PORT` |
| 🟡 Medium | No CORS policy | Add `cors` with allowlist |
| 🟡 Medium | No query param validation | Add `express-validator` |
| 🟡 Medium | No graceful shutdown | Handle `SIGTERM` |
| 🟢 Minor | Timestamp in `/health` | Remove or coarsen it |
| 🟢 Minor | No access logging | Add `morgan` |

